"n.墓志铭 【英】 n. 墓志铭 (an inscription on a tomb or gravestone) 【考】 epitaph : tombstone / motto : shield(碑文刻在墓碑上/题 铭刻在盾上) 【记】 epi(在…上)+taph(=t omb墓)→在墓碑上刻 的字→墓志铭 n. 墓志铭(刻于墓碑上用以怀念死者的碑铭); 悼文(纪念死者的短篇文学作品) 【记】epi在...上, taph = tomb(n 墓)－在墓碑上刻的字－墓志铭e出, pit(n 深坑; 陷阱): 从一个坑里出来的是墓碑, 墓碑上是墓志铭. 【类】epitaph: tombstone = motto: shield墓志铭刻在墓碑上 = 座右铭刻在盾上 【记】epi + 音：塔赋，登塔赋诗，刻在碑文上；音：哀批塔赋，伤哀地批文在塔壁上赋诗 + graph 【相关】biograph 传记 epitaph (n.)  mid-14c., from Old French epitaphe (12c.) and directly from Medieval Latin epitaphium ""funeral oration, eulogy,"" from Greek epitaphion ""a funeral oration,"" noun use of neuter of epitaphos ""of a funeral,"" from epi ""at, over"" (see epi-) + taphos ""tomb, funeral rites,"" from PIE root *dhembh- ""to bury."" Among the Old English equivalents was byrgelsleoð."
